channel.title: Speed hack *May actually have some thing here*
channel.description:
Ok well I have a very simple speed hack that I dled for some games. Its a multi purpose hack, and I decided to use it on RS.
Most speed hacks just make you lag on RS, this one didnt. I tried going fast, at first my charecter would only move from square to square slowly (with charecter sequences moving very fast) but after left one for a few moments you actually move very fast. After a moment of quick movement (2 seconds max) RS stoped responding. I tried this again while WCing, my cutting sequence was extremely fast, but I couldnt judge if I was gaining logs quicker. I was again disconnected.
I tried slow movement, worked PERFECTLY. No disconnection, BUT I have no way to judge if others saw me moving slowly, or if they are effected by it at all. One guy said I was moving slowly, but Im not sure. This hack works very nice on games like WoW, I tested on my server. But its also very detectable.
Anywho, if you want to test this some time add me *Taker332*
And if you have any insight on this please post it.
